recursive dfs is the most easily understanding, in each recursion, we add the element with the `next recursion result`. The element , referring as character in this case, has to satisfy all conditions.  

    /* DFS recursive */
    public void search(List<String> list, String str, int i, String digits, char[][] dict) {
